query: what was the overall txn amount
sql:
SELECT cast(sum(txnamount) as double) / 100 as overall_transaction_amount
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt = '2025-09-09'

query: give success count
sql:
SELECT count(*) as transaction_count
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt between '2025-08-18'
   and '2025-08-15'
   and upper(trim(currstatusdesc)) in ('SUCCESS', 'DEEMED', 'PARTIAL')

query: need count of autopay execution volume for total number of transactions having txn amount per transaction is less than 500, 400,300,200 & 100 separately
sql:
SELECT count(*) as transaction_count
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt between '2025-07-01'
   and '2025-07-31'
   and initmode = '11'
   and purposecode = '14'
   and txnamount < 500
GROUP BY txnamount < 500, txnamount < 400, txnamount < 300, txnamount < 200, txnamount < 100

query: number of p2p transactions which are having amount greater than 50000
sql:
SELECT count(*) as transaction_count
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt between '2025-08-26'
   and '2025-08-27'
   and (trim(pycode)) in ('NULL', '0000', '')
   and txnamount > 50000
   and upper(trim(currstatusdesc)) in ('SUCCESS', 'DEEMED', 'PARTIAL')

query: Give it for 26th of may 2025. need count of autopay execution volume for total number of transactions having txn amount per transaction is less than 500, 400,300,200 & 100 separately and also need of unique count of VPA against each category
sql:
SELECT count(*) as transaction_count,
       count(distinct prfvaddr) as unique_vpa_count
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt between '2025-07-01'
   and '2025-07-31'
   and initmode = '11'
   and purposecode = '14'
   and txnamount < 500
GROUP BY txnamount < 500, txnamount < 400, txnamount < 300, txnamount < 200, txnamount < 100

query: UPI rrn wise approved , td , bd qurey
sql:
SELECT custrefno as rrn,
       currstatusdesc as status,
       case when upper(trim(currstatusdesc)) in ('SUCCESS', 'DEEMED', 'PARTIAL') then 'Approved'
            when upi_masters.upi_new_errorcode_respcd_master.approvedflag = 'TD' then 'Technical Decline'
            when upi_masters.upi_new_errorcode_respcd_master.approvedflag = 'BD' then 'Business Decline' end as transaction_status
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns join upi_masters.upi_new_errorcode_respcd_master
        ON urcs_ft_txns.errorcode = upi_new_errorcode_respcd_master.error_code
WHERE  asdt between '2025-08-19'
   and '2025-08-19'
GROUP BY custrefno, currstatusdesc, upi_new_errorcode_respcd_master.approvedflag

query: upi
sql:
SELECT txnid,
       currstatusdesc,
       asdt
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt = cast(current_date as varchar)
   and upper(trim(currstatusdesc)) like '%UP%'

query: want to find the total amount transfered by each payyee
sql:

       count(*) as transaction_volume,

FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt between '2025-04-01'
   and '2025-05-31'

query: Please find transactions in which we have to fetch people who have done more than 5 transactions in a day (P2M). payer side
sql:
SELECT prdmobile as payer_mobile,
       count(*) as transaction_count
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt between '2025-08-07'
   and '2025-08-07'
   and (not trim(pycode) in ('NULL', '0000', '7407', ''))
GROUP BY prdmobile having count(*) > 5

query: To calculate the total transaction amount for each customer within a 24-hour running window
sql:
SELECT prdmobile,
       cast(sum(txnamount) as double) / 100 as total_transaction_amount
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt between '2025-08-06'
   and '2025-08-08'
GROUP BY prdmobile

query: total number of records in table upi_txn

SELECT count(*) as total_records

query: Please find transactions in which we have to fetch people who have done more than 5 transactions in a day (P2M). pls include all columns
sql:
SELECT *
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt = '2025-08-07'
   and (not trim(pycode) in ('NULL', '0000', '7407', ''))
   and (SELECT count(*)
     FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns as t
     WHERE  t.asdt = '2025-08-07'
        and t.prdmobile = upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns.prdmobile
        and (not trim(t.pycode) in ('NULL', '0000', '7407', ''))) > 5

query: Please find transactions in which we have to fetch people who have done more than 5 transactions in a day (P2M). Account no side
sql:
SELECT prdmobile as unique_users,
       count(*) as transaction_count
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt between '2025-08-07'
   and '2025-08-07'
   and (trim(prcode) in ('NULL', '0000', '')
   and not trim(pycode) in ('NULL', '0000', '7407', ''))
GROUP BY prdmobile having count(*) > 5

query: Please find transactions in which we have to fetch people who have done more than 5 transactions in a day (P2M). pls include account number column as well with their bank codes
sql:
SELECT prdmobile as payer_mobile,
       pydmobile as payee_mobile,
       praccno as payer_account_number,
       pyaccno as payee_account_number,
       prnfsparticipantid as payer_bank_code,
       pynfsparticipantid as payee_bank_code,
       count(*) as transaction_count
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt = '2025-08-07'
   and (not trim(pycode) in ('NULL', '0000', '7407', ''))
   and upper(trim(currstatusdesc)) in ('SUCCESS', 'DEEMED', 'PARTIAL')
GROUP BY prdmobile, pydmobile, praccno, pyaccno, prnfsparticipantid, pynfsparticipantid having count(*) > 5

query: To calculate the total transaction amount for each customer within a 24-hour window
sql:
SELECT custrefno,
       cast(sum(txnamount) as double) / 100 as total_transaction_amount
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt between '2025-08-06'
   and '2025-08-08'

query: B3 response code data
sql:
SELECT cast(txnamount as double) / 100 as transaction_amount,
       purposecode,
       pycode,
       prcode,
       currstatusdesc,
       errorcode,
       finalrespcode,
       benrespcode,
       asdt
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt between '2025-08-01'
   and '2025-08-07'
   and upper(trim(finalrespcode)) = 'B3'

query: B3 response code data for Central bank of India
sql:
SELECT finalrespcode,
       count(*) as transaction_count
FROM   upi_txn.urcs_ft_txns
WHERE  asdt between '2025-08-01'
   and '2025-08-07'
   and upper(trim(finalrespcode)) = 'B3' /* B3 response code */
   and upper(trim(crnfsparticipantid)) = 'CBI' /* Central Bank of India */
GROUP BY finalrespcode
